{"tid":2381393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[耶倫放鴿]富時羅素考慮將另外5間中國公司自關鍵指數中剔除","createTime":"2021-01-26T14:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T14:01:01.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"caa93c6a916703bede402bce27997305a2a0d08b","tid":2381393,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T14:01:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572494-20210126.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572494-20210126.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=f30d21c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572494-20210126.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=17cb5ea9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572494-20210126.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n富時羅素公布，正考慮是否將另外5間中國公司於關鍵指數中剔除。<br />\n<br />\n5間公司包括中廣核電力、中國核電、中國重工、浪潮國際及中化國際。<br />\n<br />\n富時羅素表示，將會繼續監控今日來自美國海外資產控制辦公室(OFAC)的所有通訊，並將在稍後時間提供指數處理情況的最新進展。"}]}